description:
Libs lose minds over Southwest pilot who may have said “Let’s go, Brandon.” Background of "Let's go Brandon" chant. Trump does Tomahawk Chop at World Series. NYC vaccine mandate kicks in; Psaki catches covid. Clay's Halloween party. Bill Maher on masks. Kristi Noem finally does what Buck told her to do on this show.
